{"word":"λιποψυχέω","slug":"λιποψυχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λιποψυχέω</b></el> <el>(λῐπο-ψῡχέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ψυχή'><el>ψυχή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to leave life, swoon</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to lack spirit, fail in courage</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}